text: Anaesthetobrium fuscoflavum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Matsushita in 1933. It is known from Taiwan.BioLib.cz - Anaesthetobrium fuscoflavum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1933
